<br />
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Color="Color.Primary">
    I’m a self-taught developer with a strong foundation in modern web technologies such as JavaScript,<br />
    React, Node.js, and Express. My journey began with freelancing, where I honed my skills working on<br />
    various projects, including web pages and NFT galleries during their peak popularity.<br />
    <br />
    I then transitioned to a full-time role at a company focused on NFT web solutions, where I gained<br />
    invaluable experience in the rapidly evolving digital space. After more than a year, I joined Accenture,<br />
    working on projects for Banco Galicia.<br />
    <br />
    At Banco Galicia, I initially contributed to the migration of self-service terminals to React, enhancing<br />
    the user experience across multiple platforms. Currently, I’m working with the Investments tribe,<br />
    leading the migration of SAP applications to React, a project that continues to challenge and inspire me<br />
    <br />
    I am passionate about leveraging technology to create impactful solutions, and I’m constantly<br />
    seeking opportunities to learn and grow in this dynamic field.<br />
    <br />
    <br />
</MudText>
